{"tid":402142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海洋公園「哈囉喂」添亡魂 男子鬼屋試瞓棺木傷頭不治","createTime":"2017-09-16T07:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T12:23:36.000Z","uid":19408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"66125dbca732650e33149a31a81fff64598354b2","tid":402142,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"海洋公園「哈囉喂」添亡魂 男子鬼屋試瞓棺木傷頭不治<br />\n <br />\n下午2時許，一名20多歲男子在香港仔海洋公園昏迷，救護員接報到場將他送院，經搶救後證實不治，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，死者一行七人趁海洋公園舉辦「哈囉喂全日祭」入場，其間他與另外兩名友人在鬼屋「活埋凶間」遊玩時，意外跌傷頭部昏迷，送院不治。<br />\n<br />\n鬼屋恐慌之最首推一人遊戲《活埋凶間》，在《活埋凶間》需要孤身上路。場景以歐洲中世紀巫毒的活埋生葬為題，遊人將各自躺在一個棺木內，並分別滑落至下層迷宮內。各人均會被滑落至不同的位置作為起點，然後在四通八達的並佈滿嘩鬼及機關的迷宮內尋找出口，可能會在途中與友人重逢，或需要獨自走完全程，並有可能被困良久，未能找到出口。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170916&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57217804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170916%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57217804&d=tfSLU24C4%2F%2FTeF1S574jaI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=10ecb686\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170916%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57217804&h=3fdcafce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170916&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57217804</a>"},{"pid":"27e99a604acf4d5a8474156625ac33db1a11a80e","tid":402142,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3739cdeb6175078213ecc971339363014bbd9c53","tid":402142,"uid":28590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:52:43.000Z","msg":"估唔到依家連香港野都信唔過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec40e896f64bf04a0e80778bc68af222e759f18a","tid":402142,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 